## Tuesday, January 24

### Readings 

1. Lavariega Monforti, Jessica, and Gabriel R. Sanchez. 2010. ["The Politics of Perception: An Investigation of the Presence and Sources of Perceptions of Internal Discrimination Among Latinos."](https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1540-6237.2010.00691.x) *Social Science Quarterly* 91(1): 245–65. ({{< fa file-pdf >}} available on Canvas)

2. Sanchez, Gabriel, Natalie Masuoka, and Brooke Abrams. 2019. ["Revisiting the Brown-Utility Heuristic: A Comparison of Latino Linked Fate in 2006 and 2016."](https://doi.org/10.1080/21565503.2019.1638803) *Politics, Groups, and Identities* 7(3): 673–83. ({{< fa file-pdf >}} available on Canvas)


